                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8635" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0261</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">843 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中蒙合作典范，带动一方发展：中色股份在蒙古的企业社会责任履行之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">A model enterprise of Sino-Mongolian cooperation, driving local development: the road of NFC&#39;s corporate social responsibility fulfillment in Mongolia</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">马建峰，陈潇杰，王琤</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国有色金属建设股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">矿冶业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会责任；利益相关者；战略性企业社会责任</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Corporate Social Responsibility; Stakeholder; Strategic corporate social responsibility</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例讲述了央企控股上市公司中色股份在国家锌精矿过度依赖进口的背景下，怀着“资源报国”和“援蒙建设”初心前往蒙古国发展海外资源开发业务，在建设“中蒙合作典范企业”的发展战略目标指引下，通过开发和建设图木尔廷—敖包锌矿带动当地经济社会发展、促进中蒙人民友好往来的过程。中色股份维护蒙方股东的权益和尽力实现合作方诉求，关怀员工的职业发展、生命安全和身心健康，利用技术优势为合作伙伴排忧解难，为蒙古国锌精矿化学分析法国家标准的更新作出贡献，响应当地居民诉求，切实保护环境、建设绿色矿山，为当地城市发展捐建基础设施、公共卫生和医疗设施，带动当地的就业、经济和相关产业发展。案例旨在帮助学生深入理解企业社会责任的内涵、动因和实施过程，理解企业如何审视自身与社会的关系，将解决社会问题与企业发展相结合，将社会责任融入企业发展战略中，分析案例对其他中国企业在海外发展的示范作用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes that under the background of excessive dependence on imports of national zinc, NFC, a listed company held by central enterprises, went to Mongolia to develop overseas mineral resource exploitation with the original aspiration of &quot;serving the country with resources&quot; and &quot;helping Mongolia construction&quot;. Under the guidance of the development strategic goal of building a &quot;model enterprise of Sino-Mongolia cooperation&quot;, the development and construction of the Tumurtiin Ovoo zinc mine drives the local economic and social development and promotes the friendly intercourse between the people of China and Mongolia. NFC protects the rights and interests of Mongolian shareholders and tries its best to realize the demands of partners, cares for the career development, life safety and physical and mental health of employees, takes technological advantages to solve problems for partners, contributes to the updates of the national standard for chemical analysis of zinc concentrate in Mongolia, responds to the demands of local residents, effectively protects the environment and builds green mines, donated infrastructure, public health and medical facilities to local urban development, and promotes local employment, economy and related industrial development. The case aims to help students to have a deep understanding of the connotation, motivation and fulfillment process of corporate social responsibility, understand how enterprises examine the relationship between themselves and society, integrate social responsibility into corporate development strategy by solving social problems, and analyze the exemplary role of the case for other Chinese enterprises&#39; overseas development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》、《企业战略》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会责任；利益相关者；战略性企业社会责任</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
